Pakistani Muslims offer prayers to celebrate the Eid al-Fitr festival in northwest Pakistan's Peshawar, July 18, 2015. Pakistani Muslims celebrate the Eid al-Fitr festival, which marks the end of the Islamic holy month of Ramadan.



